Sacyr to Invest EU2 Bln in Concessions to 2014, Expansion Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-02-16T07:05:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/sacyr-to-invest-eu2-bln-in-concessions-to-2014-expansion-says.html
  Sacyr Vallehermoso SA  will use funds
from recent capital increases to invest around 2 billion euros
($2.7 billion) in concessions until 2014 to expand outside
Spain,  Expansion  reported, citing calculations made by the
company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at 
 ablackman@bloomberg.net . 